snippet.title: The Sims 4™ Island Living: Official Gameplay
snippet.description:
Welcome to Sulani, where the sun shines bright and the nights are totally chill. Surround your Sims with sun and sand in The Sims 4 Island Living!* 

Available June 21, 2019 for PC and Mac and July 16, 2019 for Xbox One and PlayStation 4.

Learn more about this Expansion Pack: http://x.ea.com/58412.

*REQUIRES THE SIMS 4 ON APPLICABLE PLATFORM (SOLD SEPARATELY) AND ALL GAME UPDATES TO PLAY. SEE MINIMUM SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS FOR THIS EXPANSION.
